1
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,820
=Camellias=

2
00:00:53,820 --> 00:00:56,780
=Episode 3=

3
00:01:03,500 --> 00:01:05,500
(Ancestral Tablet)

4
00:01:05,680 --> 00:01:06,560
(Father Ruan Xiuyuan's Ancestral Tablet)
Father.

5
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:08,439
(Father Ruan Xiuyuan's Ancestral Tablet)
Rest assured,

6
00:01:09,040 --> 00:01:11,319
I will use the blood of the Rong clan

7
00:01:11,319 --> 00:01:13,719
to honor your spirits in heaven.

8
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:20,840
Lord Nine-Thousand is resting.

9
00:01:22,879 --> 00:01:24,640
(Nanfeng Pavilion)
I came specifically to serve you.

10
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:27,260
(Nanfeng Pavilion)

11
00:01:49,799 --> 00:01:51,280
(Strange.)

12
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:53,120
(He's not of royal blood,)

13
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:54,400
(yet I can't control him.)

14
00:02:03,799 --> 00:02:04,719
Had enough?

15
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:07,400
My Lord,

16
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:08,599
are you satisfied?

17
00:02:08,599 --> 00:02:10,039
You've got skills.

18
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:11,439
Found me so quickly.

19
00:02:12,639 --> 00:02:14,879
Oh no. He was waiting for me.

20
00:02:22,879 --> 00:02:24,360
Still trying to control me?

21
00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:27,240
How could that be?

22
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:28,319
I

23
00:02:28,639 --> 00:02:30,400
only wish to serve you.

24
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:50,319
What are you doing, My Lord?

25
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:57,159
Didn't you say you wanted me?

26
00:02:57,159 --> 00:02:58,719
I'm giving you the chance.

27
00:02:59,919 --> 00:03:01,240
Of course I want this.

28
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:04,719
I just worry your body

29
00:03:04,719 --> 00:03:06,319
might not handle it.

30
00:03:06,319 --> 00:03:08,360
You've lived in a dungeon.

31
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:10,759
You must know nothing
of intimacy between men and women.

32
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:14,719
Let me teach you.

33
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:20,039
(What's wrong with him?
Why is he acting so strange?)

34
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:31,560
(So this was all for show.)

35
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:47,960
My Lord,

36
00:03:48,759 --> 00:03:50,840
I have my ways too.

37
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,159
He's gone.

38
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:54,960
You touched me for so long.

39
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:56,639
Did you find the pendant?

40
00:04:02,439 --> 00:04:04,800
My Lord, you're no ordinary man.

41
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:07,400
I can't read your mind at all.

42
00:04:10,719 --> 00:04:12,000
Then you lose.

43
00:04:13,719 --> 00:04:15,319
But after the past few days,

44
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,800
you must believe

45
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:19,560
that I possess the Divine Power.

46
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,680
Besides,

47
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:22,120
whatever you command,

48
00:04:22,759 --> 00:04:24,800
I will give my all.

49
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:29,600
You mentioned before
that the Divine Power

50
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:31,319
can control people's minds.

51
00:04:32,639 --> 00:04:34,519
Can it control anyone?

52
00:04:36,079 --> 00:04:37,000
Not everyone.

53
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:39,759
Servants and young noble ladies,

54
00:04:39,759 --> 00:04:42,079
they're ordinary-minded.

55
00:04:42,079 --> 00:04:43,959
I can easily manipulate them.

56
00:04:46,319 --> 00:04:48,199
But someone like you,

57
00:04:48,199 --> 00:04:50,120
with a will as strong

58
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:52,240
as iron walls,

59
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:54,360
I can't.

60
00:04:56,079 --> 00:04:56,800
Stop it.

61
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:58,000
Go back.

62
00:04:59,319 --> 00:05:00,600
I'll take you to the palace tomorrow.

63
00:05:04,279 --> 00:05:07,160
(Taiji Hall)
Dress as a servant and stay close to me.

64
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,319
Remember.

65
00:05:08,319 --> 00:05:09,399
Do not draw attention.

66
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,639
Yes.

67
00:05:13,079 --> 00:05:14,839
I'll follow your lead, My Lord.

68
00:05:18,319 --> 00:05:20,800
I heard you spent last night
in the Dragon's Embrace.

69
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:22,360
With such a fine body,

70
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,920
you may have all the skills,

71
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:26,439
but I fear you lack the strength.

72
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:30,959
General Rong Xiu, you must have
eyes in the back of your head.

73
00:05:32,839 --> 00:05:34,839
You know my every move.

74
00:05:34,839 --> 00:05:36,360
Indeed.

75
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:37,560
When hunting the other day,

76
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,680
I spotted this jade bi

77
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:40,240
at first glance.

78
00:05:41,079 --> 00:05:42,040
His Majesty

79
00:05:42,439 --> 00:05:43,600
will be delighted.

80
00:05:45,439 --> 00:05:47,600
I fear it's just a crafted illusion.

81
00:05:48,199 --> 00:05:49,639
A skilled artisan's work.

82
00:05:49,639 --> 00:05:50,879
Don't you understand, My Lord?

83
00:05:51,199 --> 00:05:52,480
In this world,

84
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:53,680
sometimes,

85
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:54,800
right and wrong

86
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:56,759
don't matter.

87
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:22,040
Such a massive jade bi.

88
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:24,639
Presenting this will surely
delight His Majesty.

89
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:31,279
I was hunting a few days ago

90
00:06:31,439 --> 00:06:32,920
when a nine-colored deer led the way

91
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:34,399
(Diligence in Governance)
and revealed this jade bi.

92
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:36,360
It must be a divine blessing,

93
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,720
a sign of Your Majesty's glory

94
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:38,720
lasting ten thousand generations.

95
00:06:47,199 --> 00:06:47,759
What?

96
00:06:47,759 --> 00:06:49,319
It's cracked! How did it break?

97
00:06:49,319 --> 00:06:50,079
How dare you!

98
00:06:50,759 --> 00:06:51,199
General.

99
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:54,199
How could he?

100
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:57,360
A broken jade presented
to His Majesty?

101
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:58,120
Yeah.

102
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:59,360
That's supreme disrespect!

103
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:03,079
(Right and wrong don't matter.)

104
00:07:03,079 --> 00:07:05,519
(Those are your own words.)

105
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:18,120
(Break the jade bi.)

106
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:24,040
(Now's my chance to leave.)

107
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:27,319
Isn't this openly defying the Emperor?

108
00:07:27,319 --> 00:07:30,000
How can a flawed piece
symbolize His Majesty's authority,

109
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:32,360
even the nation's fate?

110
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:34,199
Before entering the palace,

111
00:07:34,199 --> 00:07:35,360
I inspected it thoroughly.

112
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:36,639
The jade was flawless.

113
00:07:36,639 --> 00:07:37,839
This is suspicious.

114
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:38,879
I beg Your Majesty

115
00:07:38,879 --> 00:07:39,920
to grant me a few days.

116
00:07:40,319 --> 00:07:41,560
I will get to the bottom of this.

117
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:51,319
You must be

118
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:53,199
exhausted from these past few days.

119
00:07:53,319 --> 00:07:54,680
Take a good rest.

120
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:55,600
This matter,

121
00:07:55,879 --> 00:07:56,759
let it go.

122
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:57,839
Thank you, Your Majesty.

123
00:08:13,439 --> 00:08:14,759
(I should have known)

124
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,680
(she wouldn't behave.)

125
00:08:32,879 --> 00:08:33,960
Consort Yu!

126
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:35,759
Mercy, Consort Yu!

127
00:08:35,759 --> 00:08:36,679
Consort Yu!

128
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:38,679
Why are you still alive?

129
00:08:41,159 --> 00:08:42,600
Holy Maiden,

130
00:08:42,879 --> 00:08:44,799
I had nothing to do
with your sister's death!

131
00:08:53,279 --> 00:08:55,279
You were my sister's personal maid.

132
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:57,200
She died,

133
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:59,480
yet you still live.

134
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:00,879
Do you expect me to believe

135
00:09:00,879 --> 00:09:02,240
you had nothing to do with it?

136
00:09:02,639 --> 00:09:04,080
Even if you don't speak,

137
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:07,000
I can uncover the truth.

138
00:09:07,759 --> 00:09:08,919
I'll talk!

139
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:11,559
Consort Rong forced me
to plant the Zhao Gu worm!

140
00:09:11,559 --> 00:09:12,840
I had no choice!

141
00:09:14,679 --> 00:09:16,000
You sacrificed my sister

142
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,279
to save yourself!

143
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:20,919
Then you will join her in death!

144
00:09:27,759 --> 00:09:28,879
Join her.

145
00:09:30,039 --> 00:09:31,399
Join her.

146
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:34,279
Join her. Join her.

147
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:35,960
Join her.

148
00:09:46,279 --> 00:09:49,639
(Sang, even if I die today,)

149
00:09:50,279 --> 00:09:52,440
(I will make sure all who harmed you)

150
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:55,200
(join you in the underworld.)

151
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:05,720
Who goes there?

152
00:10:08,799 --> 00:10:09,360
My Lord!

153
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:09,960
My Lord!

154
00:10:11,799 --> 00:10:13,480
She offended me.

155
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:15,639
Offending Lord Nine-Thousand,
she deserves death.

156
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:16,679
Take her.

157
00:10:16,679 --> 00:10:17,159
Yes.

158
00:10:22,679 --> 00:10:24,720
How dare she offend the Lord?
She deserves death!

159
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:25,440
Take her!

160
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:31,840
Reporting, Your Highness,

161
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:33,279
the inner palace guards report

162
00:10:33,559 --> 00:10:35,200
that the maid who served Jiang Yusang

163
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:37,840
somehow offended
Lord Nine-Thousand today

164
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:39,600
and was executed.

165
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:45,480
She's here.

166
00:10:49,639 --> 00:10:51,039
Spring has come.

167
00:10:51,919 --> 00:10:53,799
Send some peach blossom cakes

168
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:56,120
to my brother's manor.

169
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:56,919
Yes.

170
00:11:09,480 --> 00:11:10,000
General,

171
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:13,840
peach blossom cakes from Consort Rong.

172
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:18,080
Zhaohua is so thoughtful.

173
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:20,159
She knows my favorite

174
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:22,480
is peach blossom cakes.

175
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:50,039
If not for Zhaohua

176
00:11:50,039 --> 00:11:52,600
insisting on marrying that darn emperor,

177
00:11:54,039 --> 00:11:55,720
I would never have given everything

178
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:57,000
to help him take the throne.

179
00:12:00,039 --> 00:12:01,440
And yet,

180
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:04,279
not only does he mistreat her,

181
00:12:04,279 --> 00:12:06,440
but he's also unfaithful.

182
00:12:15,559 --> 00:12:16,960
Zhaohua, rest assured,

183
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:18,480
I won't let anyone

184
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,559
dim your glory.

185
00:12:42,740 --> 00:12:44,140
♪The moon sinks in the west♪

186
00:12:44,620 --> 00:12:46,060
♪The cold lamp burns low♪

187
00:12:46,260 --> 00:12:49,380
♪No one knocks upon the mountain gate♪

188
00:12:49,700 --> 00:12:53,500
♪Snow-white winds and moonlight
touch me first♪

189
00:12:56,460 --> 00:12:58,180
♪Pear blossoms fill the courtyard♪

190
00:12:58,180 --> 00:12:59,700
♪Yet love and hate entwine♪

191
00:13:00,060 --> 00:13:03,460
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

192
00:13:03,460 --> 00:13:07,460
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

193
00:13:08,620 --> 00:13:11,780
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

194
00:13:11,780 --> 00:13:15,340
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

195
00:13:15,340 --> 00:13:17,660
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

196
00:13:17,660 --> 00:13:21,860
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

197
00:13:22,300 --> 00:13:23,940
♪The green lamp sheds no light♪

198
00:13:23,940 --> 00:13:25,460
♪Upon one who entered the path♪

199
00:13:25,460 --> 00:13:28,660
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

200
00:13:29,060 --> 00:13:30,980
♪In dreams, it's you♪

201
00:13:30,980 --> 00:13:32,380
♪Beyond dreams, no one♪

202
00:13:32,380 --> 00:13:35,700
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

203
00:13:35,700 --> 00:13:39,100
♪I can't forget the stars in your eyes♪

204
00:13:39,100 --> 00:13:42,660
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

205
00:13:42,660 --> 00:13:45,900
♪In this mortal world, there is only us♪

206
00:13:45,900 --> 00:13:49,340
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪
